1. Otvorite prozor da uđe malo *vazduha*. (Open the window to let some *air* in.)
2. Izgleda da je *vazduh* zagađen danas. (It seems that the *air* is polluted today.)
3. Vožnja balonom je jedan od načina da se oseti lepota *vazduha*. (Hot air balloon ride is one way to experience the beauty of *air*.)
4. Novi filteri za vazduh poboljšaće kvalitet *vazduha* u sobi. (New air filters will improve the quality of the *air* in the room.)
5. Otvori usta i udahni *vazduh* duboko. (Open your mouth and take a deep breath of *air*.)
6. Klima uređaj omogućava regulisanje temperature i vlažnosti *vazduha*. (Air conditioner enables regulation of temperature and humidity of the *air*.)
7. Sveti Sava je bio veliki borac za čist *vazduh* i vodu. (Saint Sava was a great advocate for clean *air* and water.)
8. Čovek može da preživi samo nekoliko minuta bez *vazduha*. (A person can only survive a few minutes without *air*.)
9. Lopta je bila puna *vazduha*, ali se ispraznila nakon što je pogodila oštru stenu. (The ball was full of *air*, but it deflated after hitting a sharp rock.)
10. *Vazduh* u planinama je svež i čist. (The *air* in the mountains is fresh and clean.)